{
  "stem": "10353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He says, 'Your brother, Israel'-- which [INAUDIBLE] you might remember-- 'needs great healing.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the last time I heard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] My other sister, that I told you that was in Cluj, that was arrested, she was eventually put in a-- in-- into a camp for aliens.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in-- in 1944, that was in May-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] towards the end of May, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the way I know it, they were-- they were deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The entire city of Satu Mare was deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The rumor was that they were resettled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, that was the official-- the official version, that they were resettled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they are apparently, they are being given some very nice place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we later, of course, found out that they were deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As for myself, I was in the work brigade, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had the document as a-- conscript.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a conscript, I-- I was under military rule.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was under military rule, and all I had to do is to show that-- that summons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was-- that was official.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that, of course, applied to everybody that was conscripted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- on this document, they could only go to that particular place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't go to any other place, but only to report to-- to whatever place we were conscripted to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- OK, from [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yolsva ?], we were transferred to Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's a city in Hungary-- M-I-S-K-O-L-C.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there we were assigned to a military camp of artillery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were in charge-- we were in charge of cleaning up their mechanical things, and to dig ditches and fortifications, and you name it, that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were about 240 to 250 in this particular brigade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were known as such.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A hundred.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Number 107/23.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was our number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You belonged to that brigade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And life was tolerable there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We-- we worked, but--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were fed by the military, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No shortage, as far as that goes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we arrive into Miskolc exactly when they were rounding-- rounding up the ghetto and putting them into the wagons, to the freight-- to the freight cars.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto at Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As a matter of fact, half of our brigade belonged-- half our brigade consisted of young men from Miskolc, that their hometown was Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Miskolc and they heard that they are being deported, that the Germans are-- and the Hungarians, they did it in conjunction-- were rounding up the Jews and they're taking them away in freight trains, five of our comrades ventured out.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went AWOL.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they went to see their parents, you know, to say goodbye to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were caught, and they were also thrown into the-- into the freight cars, and we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But again, we couldn't conceive the idea that something very tragic is happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the rumor was, again, they're resettling, and-- and they are going to be put into a nice place, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, you know, there are even some-- certain postcards came back with picturesque-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] picturesque postcards saying that they are in a very nice place and that they are in good order, and nothing is happening.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Which was, of course, wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, they were forced to write these cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in Miskolc until about [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] middle to end of August.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was lucky because I became the chief-- the commander-- commanding officer's boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was his helper, and I was with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I cooked for him and I cleaned his laundry and shined his boots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I was an officer's boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I didn't have to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was just constantly with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wherever he went, I-- I went with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I had it fairly, fairly good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 19-- like I said, towards the end of August, we were transferred to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put into a-- into a factory that was producing cases for anti-aircraft shells.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, that was the duty of the-- of the brigade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But by that time, Budapest was bombed constantly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was bombed constantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we endured some horrific, horrific bombardment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that area where we were, that was a factory area, a highly industrialized area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was being targeted right along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember one Sunday morning, we were so heavily bombarded.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
